</div><div class="author"></div>
    <p>You'll have to store the coin codes somewhere - there's ways to locate those too: it's called computer forensics and it has some <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2uGMmo1Fm3o" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">pretty amazing tricks</a> up its sleeve too.</p>
